description: Eggrollin is a mobile eatery serving up authentic Filipino street food in Olympia.  Their signature item, Lumpia, is available as Beef, Chicken, Veggie-Tofu, Shanghai Pork, and the newest addition to their Lumpia family: Bacon. Other menu items include Halo-Halo, made with sweet coconut shreds, pineapple gel, jackfruit, sweet palm gel, sweet tapioca ball, cane sugar, crushed ice and evaporated milk, Filipino Chicken BBQ Sticks,  Dynamite: made using green chilis stuffed with seasoned ground pork and pepper jack cheese covered in lumpia wrapper, BBQ Pork Siopao, and a slew of other Filipino favorites.
name: Eggrollin
